      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a dependable daily driver or long-distance traveler. While the exterior paint remains vibrant, there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light wear on the driver's seat bolster consistent with careful use. All electronics and climate control systems are fully functional, and the car has a clean service record showing regular oil changes and brake maintenance. Buyers can expect a solid, road-ready vehicle that requires no immediate repairs.",
