      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to go! It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is looking for someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 34500.0,
