      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a driver-focused BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine. This example maintains excellent mechanical integrity, with the high-pressure VANOS system recently serviced and the rear subframe assembly reinforced to mitigate common chassis fatigue. The naturally aspirated power plant breathes through individual throttle bodies, delivering linear torque to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and an M-variable limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains true, benefitting from refreshed bushings and dampers that preserve the car's legendary turn-in response. While the finish displays minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and structural components are robust, making this a prime candidate for an enthusiast who prioritizes tactile performance and mechanical provenance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
