    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and is ready for its next adventure? This car is in wonderful shape and drives like a dream! It\u2019s been super reliable for me, and I\u2019ve made sure to keep it looking sharp and running smoothly. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out for a fun weekend getaway, you're going to absolutely love being behind the wheel of this one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
